## Description of the Feature

Clearly describe the feature you are requesting. What should be added or changed?

Example: "An inventory system with drag-and-drop functionality."

---

## Purpose / Benefit

Why should this feature be added? What problem does it solve or what value does it provide?

Example: "Players can organize items more easily, improving usability."

